Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:28.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ちょっとブルー　Weakness「but happy」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:32.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,けど君が居るから　Being saved
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,無駄な時間なんて無い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:35.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,雨上がる空をWaiting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Check it out　見上げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:42.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Courage is in two worlds\Nそう Together now
